<P>AN ACCOUNT OF THE CONVERSION OF AN INDIAN. IN A LETTER TO A FRIEND.</P>
<Q>Of truth I perceive that God is no respector of persons but in every nation he that feareth him and worketh righteousness, is accepted of him.</Q>
