<HEAD>PREFACE.</HEAD>
<OPENER><SALUTE>To the Reader,</SALUTE></OPENER>
<P>ALTHOUGH the following account has been publi|&s;hed in Europe; It apppears probable to me that a republication of it here may be u&s;eful. Becau&s;e it con|tains an evidence of the reality of the religion of <HI>JESUS CHRIST</HI>: which at this time is di&s;belived and held in contempt by many. From a de&s;ire to promote the intere&s;ts of piety, I venture to &s;end it forth: earne&s;tly wi&s;hing that every reader may be edified end profited by it.</P>
<CLOSER><SIGNED>J. B.</SIGNED>
<DATELINE><HI>New-York,</HI>
<DATE><HI>Nov. 29. 1794.</HI></DATE></DATELINE></CLOSER>
